data.description: Welcome to where comfort and convenience meet in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath single-family manufactured home. Nestled on an expansive lot measuring  about 1/2 an acre, this property offers a serene retreat in a sought-after Livingston neighborhood  Step inside to discover a spacious interior boasting approximately 1,280 square feet of living space. The open-concept design creates an inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining guests.  The well-appointed kitchen features newer appliances, providing the perfect space for culinary adventures.    Relax and unwind in the comfortable master suite with a private en-suite bathroom, offering a peaceful oasis for restful nights.  This home has been nicely updated, with fresh paint and new laminate floors throughout, ensuring a modern, move-in-ready experience. Say goodbye to carpet, and embrace the beauty of easy-to-maintain flooring.  The partially fenced yard features a wooden privacy fence, providing a sense of seclusion and security. The covered rear carport is a versatile space that transforms into a fantastic outdoor entertainment area, perfect for BBQs and gatherings with family and friends.   A convenient storage shed on the property offers ample space for your outdoor equipment and tools.  This home is in excellent shape and could come fully furnished, offering a turnkey opportunity for those looking to start anew without the hassle of moving furniture.
